CINNAMOM specializes in fresh, baked, homemade, Old-fashioned cinnamon rolls. These gourmet rolls are made from scratch daily using our special family recipe and shipped straight from Mom's kitchen to Yours! Now offered with over 40 toppings to choose from, these make the perfect gifts for Mother and Father's Day, Birthdays, Business gifts, Christmas morning and other holidays. Of course, they are great for the "hard to buy for person" on your gift list and are perfect for any occasion. What can be better than a yummy, soft, warm, spicy cinnamon roll topped with your choice of frosting for any season, and for any reason? These cinnamon rolls are guaranteed to be the very best you've ever had! Shipped anywhere in the United States in 6-packs of Jumbo cinnamon rolls with frostings and toppings on the side, these amazing rolls are the perfect way to spoil yourself or somebody else who appreciates good old-fashioned quality.
